482
00:37:59,886 --> 00:38:06,189
So the city keeps track of what they've done on their end through these figures, and they have reported 1,768

483
00:38:07,922 --> 00:38:11,083
changes in lead lines since 2005.

484
00:38:11,723 --> 00:38:29,686
